</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>If the married woman sees that she is visiting the house of a deceased person who was famous in his life in a scientific field, then the dream foretells her that one of her sons will have a great and prestigious position, and the dream also indicates a move to a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" >new home</a> that is better. </p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><strong>Dream Interpretation of a Living Person Visiting the Dead in Their Home for a Pregnant Woman</strong></h2>
<p>The pregnant woman's visit to the deceased in their home, and it is organized and clean, is evidence that the coming period of her life will be more stable, and she will be able to get rid of all the pains and problems that control her.  Her current health condition is the burial of the family.</p>
<p>If the vision has a close relationship with the deceased's family, then this indicates that she will actually visit this house soon, but if she feels heavy in her chest when visiting this house, then this is evidence that she is bearing many responsibilities, which make her feel weak all the time.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
