<p>As for the living person visiting the deceased but in the hospital, it is an indication of the arrival of a message to the dreamer related to this deceased or his family, as interpreters see that the dreamer will enter into charitable work in the near future because he wants to deal with God Almighty in good deeds.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
