<h2><strong>A Dead Father Visiting His Daughter in a Dream</strong></h2>
<p>The dead father's visit to his daughter is a sign that she will enjoy a peaceful and stable life and that God Almighty will give her good offspring.  The deceased father who visits his married daughter's house is evidence that she will excel greatly in her work and that she will achieve many achievements in her life and be a source of pride for her family.  Signs of anger appeared on the father's face, which indicates that the daughter has committed many sins and must repent from them.</p>
